    <memoCHS>&lt;p&gt;台泥公司碳捕集技?，?中?大?高度重?，中?水泥网2014年第11期期刊??「气候目?倒逼 水泥工?碳?排」??，以特?????「碳捕集：???室气体排放的新技?」，并以台泥公司?案例，介?在水泥行?，台泥公司与工研院?能所合作研?「?回路捕?二氧化碳技?先?型??厂」，在碳捕集技?的研?与?用上已?走在了前列，?全球同?型技?中?模最大。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.taiwancement.com/upload/news/20150226_01/file/中國水泥網2014年第11期碳捕集專題.pdf"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;「碳捕集：???室气体排放的新技?」?????容??： (?据源：中?水泥网期刊2014年第11期)&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</memoCHS>
    <memoen>&lt;p&gt;Carbon Capture Technology from Taiwan Cement Corporation was highly recognized by China. The journal from China Cement Net published in November 2014 reported as monograph with title &amp;ldquo;Carbon capture, the new technology to slow down warm house gas release&amp;rdquo;. The story reported Taiwan Cement Corporation as a case study with introduction of CCS leading pioneer plant worked between TCC and ITRI. The plant was an benchmark on carbon capture application and research and also be the largest among similar technology.&lt;/p&gt;
