    <memoen>&lt;p&gt;Energy and environmental issues were more and more emphasized, Taiwan Cement Company echoes energy saving from the government.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Taiwan Cement Company was certificated by SGS as the first cement company to build up ISO50001 energy management system. The company was honored by Ministry of Economic Affair, SGS and Taiwan Green Productivity Foundation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mr. Koo, Chairman of Taiwan Cement Corporation stated energy consumption is always concentrated in cement production process. Not only it occupies major portion of cost, but also &amp;ldquo;environmental is not cost but responsibility&amp;rdquo; as core operating thinking. Public can see the activeness for environment and energy consumption from the TCC Group. The company always endeavors in energy saving and applies new facility and technology to improve the efficiency of energy utilization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After effort of the team, Taiwan Cement Company was certificated by SGS as the first cement company to build up ISO50001 energy management system. The company was honored by Ministry of Economic Affair, SGS and Taiwan Green Productivity Foundation. At the same time, we acknowledged it is not the end of mission, but the beginning point of continuous development . TCC will keep ISO spirit to push energy efficiency to achieve going concern of environment and profit making.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;98% of energy was relied on import to Taiwan, besides that, power can not be imported from other countries, the safety of power is a big issue to Taiwan. Government will push power saving campaign to save one percent power consumption.&lt;/p&gt;
