&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width="557" height="285" alt="" src="/upload/news/2015121174657_57/image/news20150121.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</memoCHS>
    <memoen>&lt;p&gt;Members of TCC Group applied various monitors and maangements followed by environmeantl valuation committee. But for social responsibility and operating core thinking from importance of Hoping Cement Industrial Zone and environematnl is not cost but responsibility. TCC Group actvitely allocated resource and entrusted National Taiwan Ocean University on environmental integrated survey project. The related data will be referred by enterprises, authority and acadamic research for long term study for nieghborhood ecological planning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The area of the survey is from Nan Ao river to Li Wu river with three years term to be more representaive and fulfill the control of neighborhood area changes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The scope of the project includes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1. data base building up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2. Ocean ecological changes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3. Ocean geoagraphy analysis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4. water release impact analysis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5. heavy mental background analysis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6. quality of environent integrated analysis&lt;/p&gt;
