    <memoen>&lt;p&gt;On 18 December,2014, Chairman of Summit Conference for entrepreneurs between Straits Taiwan, Mr. Vincent Siew visited Dr. Cecilia Koo Botanic Conservation Center with couple of Mr. Tseng, Chairman of Conference China.. Mr.Tseng appreciated the contribution for reservation of variability for plants from the Center and also stated the reservation must be emphasized in China.&lt;/p&gt;
