    <memoen>&lt;p&gt;Hosted by Phenix New Media and China National Radio, Mr. Leslie KOO, Chairman of TCC Group, was honored as &amp;ldquo;Chinese Economic Leader for year 2014&amp;rdquo; among 30 candidates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The speech from Mr. KOO, he mentioned &amp;ldquo;Environmental is responsibility&amp;rdquo; in different occasions and that stands for the development of the TCC Group. The core enterprise value of the Group is sustainability for operation and earth. Sustainability for earth means as long as development of enterprises, the enterprises must keep clean air, water and sufficient food without destroying balance of the all ecology. Civilization of human being can be going forward with rebirth of the earth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Under this thinking, TCC Group strongly considers actively fulfill environmental policy from the government and maintain the natural and human surrounding during any products outputs. Mr. KOO thinks there is no any opportunity if the industry sacrifices environment to exchange its success.&lt;/p&gt;
