    <memoCHS>&lt;p&gt;大?地?中?水泥???展示中?水泥行?上市公司的???力，鼓?水泥企?做优做?，培育具有????力和影?力的??企?，推?水泥行?健康持??展，本?公?、公正、科?的原?，根据水泥?量、利???、??、市值等四?年度??指?，与???家和?券金融界的?家共同?行了2014年中?水泥上市公司?合?力??。本公司之?投?公司台泥??集?于30大水泥上市公司中????排名第八名。&lt;/p&gt;</memoCHS>
    <memoen>&lt;p&gt;China Cement Association encourages cement plays to be more competitive as global leading enterprises and continuously push healthier development in China cement business. The association based on shipment, profitability, assets and market cap as indicators to evaluate the comprehensive strength. TCCIH, subsidiary of TCC was ranked #8 in this evaluation.&lt;/p&gt;</memoen>
