    <memoen>&lt;p&gt;From Institutional Investors Magazine, Taiwan Cement Corporation was awarded one of the most honored companies among all- Asia Executive Team for third year. CEO and IR Professional were recognized by investment community and rated top 3 in industrial sector. TCC is the only one cement name in Taiwan and also the only one from non tech industry. Besides that, TCC is the only private owned cement company on the list in Great China region.&lt;/p&gt;</memoen>
