    <memoen>&lt;p&gt;Taipei Medical University granted Honored PhD to Mr. Koo on 9th/June. Mr. KOO led TCC Group 10 years ago with discipline, team and execution spirit to recreate glory of TCC Group. After fighting all difficulties, TCC becomes #1 in Taiwan, #6 in China and # 12 globally cement play. Mr. Koo appreciated the honor from the University and thanked for the tolerance and support from mother, wife and children and assistant from the colleagues. During the speech, Mr. Koo shared experience with graduated regarding never surrender and expected all graduated as superstar on their owned life stage. He also encouraged all the graduated be fully prepared for the future.&lt;/p&gt;
