    <memoen>&lt;p&gt;TCC&amp;rsquo;s always keeps &amp;ldquo;Environmental is responsibility but not cost&amp;rdquo; as core business guidance and further transfers into commercial opportunities. TCC&amp;rsquo;s plants received China Environmental Labeling and China Low Carbon Product certification in the beginning of year 2014.&lt;/p&gt;
