    <memoen>&lt;p&gt;Taiwan Cement Corporation was elected as major benchmark for project &amp;ldquo; 2025 Taiwan industrial new vision, vision in future: pattern of vision development and vision case study&amp;rdquo; by Ministry of Economic Affairs.&lt;/p&gt;
